data.description: Welcome to your delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home! You'll appreciate the modern features throughout the home, including newer tile, flooring and fixtures in both bathrooms. The home is also equipped with a charming, modernized kitchen! Stunning oak hardwood floors harmonize with the soothing neutral paint palette, recessed lighting, and the recently updated vinyl insulated windows allowing natural light to pour in! This home is ready for you to move right in! Nestled on a spacious corner lot within a tranquil cul-de-sac, there's ample space for entertaining or simply enjoying the outdoors in the serene and picturesque setting. Plus, you'll have the convenience of East Brainerd living with swift access to Hamilton Place. Welcome home!
